{"tid":1912680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對'四眼姨姨話佢個朋友831個日係太子站俾黑警打死左'一POST有感","createTime":"2020-03-06T08:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T16:39:30.000Z","uid":26770,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e78816f6fdbfc214f284d194eac571ee415c40","tid":1912680,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"原文<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1577080/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1577080/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n9月6號晚HKFP訪問左一個四眼姨姨<br />\n四眼姨姨話佢個朋友831個日係太子站俾黑警打死左<br />\n佢朋友父母好大年紀<br />\n去差館要返個女條屍個陣俾黑警軟禁埋<br />\n<br />\n但其後四眼姨姨9月7號有條好可疑既聲帶同相流出<br />\n把聲係四眼姨姨用生硬帶驚恐既聲線話自己都係聽返黎叫人唔好信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但整POST最大重點係當時的流出相</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/gaj9wK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgaj9wK2.jpg&h=ff0b0024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/ze417ir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fze417ir.jpg&h=9a5321ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c85931fa072db8f72b32317e49ffe44f057a593","tid":1912680,"uid":26770,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"1 呢一個A4 PAPER加電腦特大字係香港警魔記招展示證物的方式<br />\n<br />\n2 極可能四眼姨姨遭香港警魔捉走毒打同侵犯後迫於無奈錄音,語氣感覺到好驚慌<br />\n<br />\n3我同意原POST推測四眼姨姨已遭毒手"},{"pid":"514c852ea697772e1734415b2cd8198f695370f9","tid":1912680,"uid":313514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb3bbee6dac1e25f94ca6ae87d27d684c181361f","tid":1912680,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"54a67e1793ce9bb204a605e79652e64b8ec2a60c","tid":1912680,"uid":61547,"like":16,"dislike":42,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"一張電腦印既紙就係證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n